maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.orig: We offer higher quality equipment made in Rookie Harbor!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.text: Nous offrons des équipements de qualité supérieure, fabriqué localement à \v[area.rookie-harbor.name] !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.orig: Yes, yes, this interior design might seem familiar to you, but it really is the details that make the difference.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.text: Oui, bon, la décoration intérieure t'est peut-être un peu familière, mais c'est vraiment les petits détails qui changent tout.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.orig: Also we are currently remodelling.\. So, you buying or what?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.text: Ah et on est aussi en train de refaire la déco.\. Sinon, vous voulez acheter quelque chose ou pas ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.orig: We offer higher quality equipment made in Rookie Harbor!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.text: Nous offrons des équipements de qualité supérieure, fabriqué localement à \v[area.rookie-harbor.name] !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.orig: Hey! We offer special items, supported by only the finest of backers.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-equip-north.jso.text: Hé ! Nous offrons des objets spéciaux, uniquement grâce à nos soutiens généreux !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.orig: Hey there, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. You can make yourself comfortable but you better also order something.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.text: Coucou, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Tu peux t'installer ici, mais tu ferais mieux de commander quelque chose.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.orig: Ah, finally, another \v[lore.title.seeker] visiting my humble establishment.\. Are you the one with the new supplies?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.text: Ah, enfin, un autre \v[lore.title.seeker] qui visite mon petit établissement.\. Tu ne serais pas celle qui a mes provisions ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.orig: About time.\. That Mr. Nomsworth promised me those ingredients hours ago.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.text: Il était temps.\. Ce M. Bonmange m'a promis ces ingrédients il y a plusieurs heures.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.orig: Makes me wonder why we even pay fancy paperpushers like him for just doing some calls anyway.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.text: On se demande pourquoi on a besoin de payer des bureaucrates comme lui, si c'est juste pour qu'ils passent des coups de fils à droite à gauche.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.orig: Next time I might just contact those doing the real work myself.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.text: La prochaine fois, j'appellerai les gens moi-même.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.orig: Anyway, I'll send him a confirmation about the job.\. You better go back to him to get your reward.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.text: Bon, en tout cas, je vais lui envoyer une confirmation que le travail a été fait.\. Tu devrais le revoir pour obtenir ta récompense.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.orig: I've already transmitted the okay to that good-for-nothing.\. Better go get your pay before it vanishes from his memory.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-harbor-pub.json.text: J'ai déjà transmis le reçu à ce bon-à-rien. Tu ferais mieux d'aller le voir avant qu'il n'oublie ta paye.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joy
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Joy

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Did you notice that strange device next to the Inn-Keeper?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Tu as remarqué cette machine bizarre à la réception ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Always wondered what that is.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Je me suis toujours demandé ce que c'était.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Oh, that's a Ball-Recharger!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Oh, ça ? c'est un Recharge-Boule !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Come again?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Euh, comment ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Yeah, I forgot you joined CrossWorlds a bit later.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ah oui, j'ai oublié que tu as commencé CrossWorlds un peu plus tard.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: In the first release, you had to recharge your balls once you ran out of stamina.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Dans la première version, il fallait recharger tes boules quand ton endurance était vide.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: There was even an extra gauge for that in the HUD.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Il y avait une jauge supplémentaire dans l'interface pour ça.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Really? Wow, I can't imagine having fun doing that.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Vraiment ? Je comprends pas en quoi ça pouvait être fun de faire ça.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: That's why they removed it, I guess. No one was happy.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: C'est pour ça qu'ils l'ont enlevé. Ça plaisait à personne.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: But they keep this asset in as a reminder of the old times.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Mais ils ont gardé cette vieillerie en souvenir de l'ancien temps.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Jock
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Jock

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Guid day, Lea!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Bionjour, Lea !
... Salut ?!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Kehahaha. Dornt fash yerse quine. Jean tauld me aw abit ye!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Khahaha ! Flipp' pas, gonzess'. Jean m'a porlé d'twa !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Jock
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Jock

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Aam \c[3]Jock\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Chuis \c[3]Jock\c[0] !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Shocker fur ye, huh? Heard yer speech module is broken.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ça t'surpraud hein ? Askip' ton module vocal est pété.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ye swatch loch th' cheerful lassie nonetheless.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Mais t'as l'look d'une meuf sympa en tout cas.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Keha, sae ye want tae ken somethin' abit th' \c[3]legendary bunny\c[0], aye?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Kha ! T'veux causer d'ce \c[3]lapinou légendaire\c[0] ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Alrecht, haur is whit Ah ken!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: 'Kay, J'te dis c'que j'sais.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ah heard, ye need tae fin' some sort ay roon capture device.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: J'ai cru camprendre qu't'as besoin d'trauver une espèce de treuc rond pour l'chopper.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ye can teel Jean Ah micht hae foond thes device, but she still needs somethin' else.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: J'peux dire à Jean qu'j'l'ai trouvé, mais qu'y a b'soin d'un autr' truc.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: But ah dunnae ken whit 'at is, kehahaha.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Mais j'sais pas c'que sait, khahaha.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ah will send Jean aw th' details.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: J'vais filer à Jean les détauïlles.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ye micht foond it mair when ye gab tae uir triblader mukker.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ptet' que l'autr' triblader en sait pleuss là dussus.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Jock
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Jock

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Awrite Lea, Ah send everythin' tae Jean.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: C'bon Lea. J'vais tout envauyer à Jean.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Joe le Jeunot

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Joe le Jeunot

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Salut.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Oh boy, a \v[lore.title.seeker]!\. So cool to finally meet one!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Oh, un \v[lore.title.seeker] !\. C'est trop cool d'enfin en rencontrer un !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi?!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Salut ?!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I asked for help with a really awesome investigation but you're the first to volunteer!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: J'ai demandé de l'aide pour une enquête de folie, mais tu es la première à te porter volontaire !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Well... you are, right?\. It's about some new species of \v[combat.name.hedgehog], how cool is that? Come on!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Je veux dire... tu l'es, hein ?\. C'est à propos d'une nouvelle espèce de \v[combat.name.hedgehog] ! C'est pas génial, ça ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Amazing, I see that you're with me on this!\. A true explorer!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Je suis heureux qu'on soit sur la même longueur d'onde ! Une véritable exploratrice !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Now, listen.\. We gotta go after this tribe of \v[combat.name.hedgehog]s I saw on an expedition recently.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Bon, écoute :\. Nous devons suivre les traces de ce nouveau genre de \v[combat.name.hedgehog]s que j'ai aperçu lors d'une expédition.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hey, wait!\. It's not just your normal-type \v[combat.name.hedgehog]s, oh no!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Hé, attend !\. Ce n'est pas juste des \v[combat.name.hedgehog]s normaux comme tu peux t'y attendre, oh non !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: The ones I saw must have evolved into a previously unseen \c[3]Flying-type\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ceux que j'ai vu ont dû évoluer en une espèce inconnue de \c[3]type Vol\c[0] !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I know, right?!\. No one believed me without proof and it wasn't like I could follow their footprints!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Je sais, hein ?!\. Personne ne veut me croire sans preuve et ce n'est pas comme si je pouvais suivre leurs empreintes de pas !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Now this is where you come in!\. You will need to check out \c[3]Off Road 2\c[0] in \c[3]\v[area.autumn-area.name]\c[0].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Mais c'est là que tu entres en jeu !\. Tu dois aller au \c[3]Hors Sentier 2\c[0] à \c[3]\v[area.autumn-area.name]\c[0].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I saw them grazing there before they flew away, so I'm sure that they'll return!\. Please go there quickly.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Je les ai vu brouter là avant qu'ils ne s'envolent, donc je suis sûr qu'ils vont revenir !\. Dépéche-toi d'aller là-bas.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Great!\. I will do some more searching on my own.\. We'll stay in touch over \c[3]\v[lore.title.direct-link]\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Super !\. Je vais faire plus de recherches de mon côté.\. On reste en contact via \c[3]\v[lore.title.direct-link]\c[0] !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Bye.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Bye.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [shakes head]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Whaaat?\. But you got me all excited and everything.\. Let's at least exchange numbers to stay in touch!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Quoi ?\. Mais tu me semblais partante et tout.\. Échangeons au moins nos numéros pour rester en contact !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: ...bye.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: ... Bye.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Joe le Jeunot

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Salut.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hey \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Please hurry and check out \c[3]Off Road 2\c[0] in \c[3]\v[area.autumn-area.name]\c[0].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Hé, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Tu dois vite aller au \c[3]Hors Sentier 2\c[0] à \c[3]\v[area.autumn-area.name]\c[0] et regarder ce que tu peux trouver !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I will continue my searching on my own.\. We will stay in touch over \c[3]\v[lore.title.direct-link]\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Je vais continuer mes recherches de mon côté.\. On reste en contact via \c[3]\v[lore.title.direct-link]\c[0] !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Joe le Jeunot

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Salut.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: \v[lore.title.seeker]!\. There you are again!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: \v[lore.title.seeker] !\. Te revoilà !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I have already written a report based on your adventure with the \c[3]Flying-types and their king.\. \c[0]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: J'ai déjà écrit un rapport d'après tes aventures avec les \c[3]Harissons type Vol et leur Roi\c[0].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: All those people who didn't believe me will be in for a surprise, I tell ya!\. It will rock their shorts off!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Tous ceux qui ne me croyaient pas risquent d'avoir une surprise, c'est moi qui te le dis !\. Ça va leur faire tomber le pantalon !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: That crown will be a nice trophy as well.\. Always helps to have something shiny to show.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Cette couronne sera un superbe trophée.\. Ça aide toujours de montrer des choses brillantes aux gens.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Thank you so much for your help, \v[lore.title.seeker]. I can't give you a badge but I hope this will do for a reward!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Merci beaucoup pour ton aide, \v[lore.title.seeker]. Je ne peux pas te donner une médaille, mais je suis sûr que cette récompense te suffira !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Bye!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Bye !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Yep, yep, see you around!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ouaip, ouaip, on se revoit !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-item.json/entit.orig: Hello, how can I help you?
That's quite the promotion for a sandwich.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-item.json/entit.text: C'est vraiment pas mal comme promo pour un sandwich.
Tu penses que ça vaut le coup ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-item.json/entit.orig: I prefer my good old ordinary sandwiches, really.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-item.json/entit.text: Je préfère mes bons vieux sandwichs normaux, en fait.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: Good day, Miss \v[lore.title.seeker]. I welcome you to the headquarters of the \c[3]\v[lore.title.faction-shock-rookieharbor]\c[0].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Bonne journée, Madame \v[lore.title.seeker]. Bienvenue dans le quartier général de la \c[3]\v[lore.title.faction-shock-rookieharbor]\c[0].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: If you are looking to trade, you can find goods from all over \v[lore.title.planet] here.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Si vous souhaitez marchander, vous pouvez trouver ici des biens venant de chaque recoin de \v[lore.title.planet].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: Our range of goods is sure to expand over time so you are advised to return from time to time.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Notre offre de produits va certainement s'améliorer avec le temps, donc vous devriez revenir de temps en temps.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: If you are on an assignment for our corporation, you can find the management upstairs.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Si vous avez reçu une affectation pour notre syndicat, vous pouvez trouver les manageurs à l'étage.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: I am sorry, ma'am, but this part is restricted to the staff.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Je suis désolé, madame, mais cette entrée est pour le personnel.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: I am sorry, ma'am, but this area is restricted to the staff.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Je suis désolé, madame, mais cet endroit est réservé au personnel.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: I see you have business with the board.\. In that case please go upstairs and have a nice day.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Ah je vois que vous avez une affaire avec le bureau des directeurs.\. Dans ce cas, vous pouvez les retrouver à l'étage. Passez une bonne journée.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.orig: Good day, ma'am.\. You can go upstairs.\. Have a nice day.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-gro.text: Bonjour, madame.\. Vous pouvez aller à l'étage. Passez une bonne journée.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Guard
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Garde

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Chairman Steward
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Directeur Général Steward

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Steward
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Steward

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: I am sorry, \v[lore.title.seeker] but the market is hot.\. Please do not distract me.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Je suis désolé, \v[lore.title.seeker] mais le marché bouge en ce moment et il demande toute mon attention.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Steward
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Steward

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Hi!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Salut !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Ah, good evening, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. We have been expecting you.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Ah, bonsoir, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Nous vous attendions.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Mr. Nomsworth spoke very highly of your abilities.\. Let us hope that his trust is not misplaced.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: M. Bonmange nous a favorablement parlé de vous et de vos capacités.\. Nous espérons qu'il ne s'est pas trompé.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: As you hopefully know, \v[area.rookie-harbor.name] is a central settlement with strong connections all over \v[lore.title.planet].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Comme vous le savez sûrement, \v[area.rookie-harbor.name] est un point de jonction central avec de fortes relations partout sur \v[lore.title.planet].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: There is barely a commodity that cannot be found on our mighty venues of capitalism.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Il y a peu de produits que nous ne pouvons pas obtenir à travers nos puissantes relations commerciales.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Despite this, we still lack the capacity to acquire high-quality metal without relying on the other settlements.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Malgré cela, nous manquons encore la capacité de produire du métal de haute qualité de nos propres mains.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: It will be your most urgent task to remedy this.\. I hope we can still count on your assistance?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Votre travail sera de remédier à cela le plus rapidement possible. J'espère que l'on peut encore compter sur votre assistance ?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Excellent.\. Then go to \v[area.bergen.name] and visit their trader of metalworks.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Excellent.\. Allez au \v[area.bergen.name] et visitez leur marchand de métaux.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: We have already negotiated a satisfying arrangement.\. You will fulfill our end of the bargain.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Nous avons déjà négocié un arrangement satisfaisant.\. Vous irez remplir notre part de l'accord.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Good.\. Now go and carry out your task.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Bien.\. Maintenant allez-y et accomplissez votre tâche.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Bye!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Bye !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Steward
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Steward

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Go to \c[3]\v[area.bergen.name]\c[0] and talk to their \c[3]trader of metalworks\c[0] in the \c[3]Trader's Den\c[0].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Allez au \c[3]\v[area.bergen.name]\c[0] et parlez à leur \c[3]marchand de métaux\c[0] à \c[3]l'Antre du Marché\c[0].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: He will have a task for you to fulfill.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Il aura une tâche pour vous à accomplir.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Steward
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Steward

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Hi!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Salut !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: \v[lore.title.seeker], welcome back!\. The necessary tools have already arrived and they work splendidly.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: \v[lore.title.seeker], Bienvenue à nouveau !\. Les outils nécessaires sont déjà arrivés et fonctionnent parfaitement.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: From now on, we will be able to trade higher quality metal directly in \v[area.rookie-harbor.name].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: À partir de maintenant, nous pourrons exporter du métal de haute qualité directement depuis \v[area.rookie-harbor.name].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: You have been a great help.\. Nomsworth really deserves a pat on the back for picking you.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Vous nous avez été d'une grande aide.\. Bonmange mérite vraiment une petite tape dans le dos pour vous avoir choisi.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: And you will also get your reward, of course.\. We should stay in contact for future deals.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Et vous aurez également votre récompense, bien entendu.\. Nous devrions rester en contact pour des futurs arrangements.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: [acquiesce]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Bye!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Bye !

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Steward
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Steward

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: I am sorry \v[lore.title.seeker], but the market is hot.\. Please do not distract me.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Je suis désolé, \v[lore.title.seeker] mais le marché bouge en ce moment et il demande toute mon attention.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.orig: Receptionist
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-north-trade-upp.text: Réceptionniste

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-weapon.json/ent.orig: We offer high quality equipment made in Rookie Harbor!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-weapon.json/ent.text: Nous vendons de l'équipement de haute qualité, fabriqué localement à Rookie Harbor !

maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.orig: Hi... make it quick, I think I'm gonna close soon and head to the bar...
maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.text: Salut... Soyez rapide, je pense que je vais bientôt fermer et aller au bar...

maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.orig: Good day! Do you by chance have any Sandwiches for sale?
maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.text: Bonjour ! Est-ce que par hasard, vous n'auriez pas des sandwichs ?

maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.orig: Yepp, only 2500 Credits! Should I wrap it up for you?
maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.text: Oui bien sûr, seulement \v[misc.localNum.2500] Crédits ! Je vous l'emballe ?

maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.orig: Why do they always run away? My wares are top-notch, right?
maps/rookie-harbor/special/shop.json/ent.text: Pourquoi est-ce qu'ils s'enfuient tous ? Mes marchandises sont de premier choix, non ?
